MovieList.title: Conjuring Kannappan
MovieList.name: Comedy/Horror
MovieList.about: Conjuring Kannappan is a Tamil movie starring Sathish Muthukrishnan, Regina Cassandra and Elli EvRam in prominent roles.

MovieList.title: Wonka
MovieList.name: Fantasy/Comedy/Musical
MovieList.about: Based on the extraordinary character of Charlie and the Chocolate Factory, Roald Dahl`s most iconic children`s book, Wonka tells the wondrous story of how the world`s greatest inventor, magician and chocolate-maker became the beloved Willy Wonka we know today.

MovieList.title: 80s Buildup
MovieList.name: Comedy/Fantasy
MovieList.about: 80`s Buildup is a Tamil movie starring Santhanam in the lead.

MovieList.title: Salaar : Cease Fire part-1
MovieList.name: Action/thriller
MovieList.about: Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action.

MovieList.title: Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom
MovieList.name: Adventure/Fantasy
MovieList.about: When an ancient power is unleashed, Aquaman must forge an uneasy alliance with an unlikely ally to protect Atlantis, and the world, from irreversible devastation.

MovieList.title: Parking
MovieList.name: Drama/Thriller
MovieList.about: Eswar, an IT employee, moves into a new house with his pregnant wife. Ilamparuthi, a government employee, has been living next door for over 15 years with his wife and daughter. Things take a turn when Eswar buys a car and parks it in their common parking space. Did their ego win over them or did they realize their mistake?

MovieList.title: Fight Club
MovieList.name: Action/thriller
MovieList.about: Selva, a young vibrant college student who dreams to be a footballer is frustrated with life due to lack of opportunities. He grows into an angry young man who is drawn into conflicts involving him and his family.

MovieList.title: Napoleon
MovieList.name: Action/Historical
MovieList.about: Napoleon is a spectacle-filled action epic that details the checkered rise and fall of the iconic French Emperor Napoleon Bonaparte, played by Oscar-winner Joaquin Phoenix.Against a stunning backdrop of large-scale filmmaking orchestrated by legendary director Ridley Scott, the film captures Bonaparte`s relentless journey to power through the prism of his addictive, volatile relationship with his one true love, Josephine, showcasing his visionary military and political tactics against some of the most dynamic practical battle sequences ever filmed.

MovieList.title: Joe
MovieList.name: Drama/Romantic
MovieList.about: The movie revolves around the emotional rollercoaster of love, laughter, friendships and heartbreaks in Joe`s life.

MovieList.title: The Marvels
MovieList.name: Action/Fantasy
MovieList.about: Carol Danvers aka Captain Marvel has reclaimed her identity from the tyrannical Kree and taken revenge on the Supreme Intelligence. But unintended consequences see Carol shouldering the burden of a destabilized universe.When her duties send her to an anomalous wormhole linked to a Kree revolutionary, her powers become entangled with that of Jersey City super-fan, Kamala Khan aka Ms. Marvel, and Carol`s estranged niece, now S.A.B.E.R. astronaut Captain Monica Rambeau. Together, this unlikely trio must team-up and learn to work in concert to save the universe as `The Marvels.`
